msgctxt "an4.230:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.230:0.2"
msgid "23. Duccaritavagga"
msgstr "23. Bad Conduct"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.230:0.3"
msgid "230. Duppaññasutta"
msgstr "230. Witless"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.230"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.230:1.1"
msgid ""
"… pe … Assaddho hoti, dussīlo hoti, kusīto hoti, duppañño hoti … pe … saddho "
"hoti, sīlavā hoti, āraddhavīriyo hoti, paññavā hoti—"
msgstr ""
"“A foolish person … makes much bad karma. … They’re faithless, unethical, "
"lazy, and witless. … An astute person … makes much merit. … They’re "
"faithful, ethical, energetic, and wise."

msgctxt "an4.230:1.2"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso "
"akkhataṃ anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo "
"viññūnaṃ, bahuñca puññaṃ pasavatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When an astute, competent good person has these four qualities they keep "
"themselves healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and criticized "
"by sensible people, and they make much merit.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.230:1.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
